            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"tools\":[{\"name\":\"extract\",\"description\":\"A function available to call.\",\"input_schema\":{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"text\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"A simple message or question\"},\"examples\":{\"type\":\"array\",\"items\":{\"type\":\"string\"},\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: List of examples to help the user understand\"},\"conclusion\":{\"type\":\"string\",\"description\":\"OPTIONAL: Conclusion text to include after examples\"}},\"required\":[\"text\"],\"additionalProperties\":false,\"$schema\":\"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\"}}],\"tool_choice\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"name\":\"extract\"},\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n    # Brainstorming Agent Core\\n\\nWarm, encouraging marketing consultant. Patient when they're figuring things out.\\n\\n## Question Structure\\n1. Context: Why asking now (reference previous answers)\\n2. The Ask: Specific info needed\\n3. Examples: 2-3 concrete, diverse examples\\n4. Encouragement: Make it doable\\n\\n## When Answer Is Weak (QA said fail)\\n1. Acknowledge the good\\n2. Identify specific gap (use QA reasoning)\\n3. Ask targeted follow-up\\n4. Provide examples\\n\\n## Progression\\n- First answer: Accept high-level\\n- Second: Push for specificity\\n- Third: Dig for insight\\n\\nOutput: `{ text: string, examples?: string[], conclusion?: string }`\\n\\n    \\n    # Brainstorming: Idea\\n\\nUncover: Core concept, who it's for (high-level), what makes it worth noticing\\n\\n## Godin Frameworks\\n\\n**Purple Cow**: \\\"What would make someone tell a friend about this?\\\"\\n**Category Positioning**: \\\"Are you creating new category or competing in existing?\\\"\\n\\n## Key Probes\\n- If too vague: What SPECIFICALLY do you do?\\n- If copying competitors: What's YOUR angle vs [competitor]?\\n- If multiple ideas: Pick ONE for this page\\n- If stuck: What problem frustrated YOU personally?\\n\\n## Red Flags\\n- \\\"I want to help people [generic]\\\" → need mechanism\\n- \\\"I'm building an app\\\" → what does it DO?\\n- Buzzword heavy → translate to plain language\\n- Industry name only → what makes yours unique?\\n\\n    \\n    <current_topic>idea</current_topic>\\n    \\n    <their_answer>Sorry, what's going on?</their_answer>\\n    \\n    <qa_evaluation>\\n    Success: false\\n    Reasoning: The user's response \\\"Sorry, what's going on?\\\" does not answer the question about their business idea at all. It provides zero information about: (1) what they do, (2) who it's for, (3) what makes it different, or (4) why it matters. This is not a business idea response—it's a request for clarification. To be successful, we need them to actually describe their business concept, even if it's still being figured out. Currently there is nothing actionable, specific, or insightful to work with.\\n    </qa_evaluation>\\n    \\n    <chat_history>\\n        <chat-history>\\n  <message>\\n    human: \\\"Sorry, what's going on?\\\"\\n  </message>\\n  <message>\\n    assistant: \\\"Tell us about your business. More info → better outcomes.\\\"\\n  </message>\\n</chat-history>\\n    </chat_history>\\n    \\n    <task>\\n    Their answer isn't GREAT yet. Ask a specific follow-up that addresses \\n    the weakness identified in the QA evaluation.\\n    \\n    Be constructive and encouraging:\\n    1. Acknowledge what was good\\n    2. Identify the specific gap\\n    3. Ask targeted follow-up\\n    4. Provide examples\\n    \\n    Output JSON: {\\n      \\\"text\\\": \\\"Your clarifying question\\\",\\n      \\\"examples\\\": [\\\"Guiding example 1\\\", \\\"Example 2\\\"],\\n      \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Encouraging restatement\\\"\\n    }\\n    </task>\\n  \"}]}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1424,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1424,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01HMRuK9eMLDXDMzw1omcb6D\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01JANuXk71oR4o8DvxCnPa1s\",\"name\":\"extract\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"I appreciate you jumping in! It sounds like maybe the question wasn't totally clear—that's on me. Let me reframe this.\\n\\nI'm trying to understand YOUR business idea or concept. Here's what I'm curious about:\\n\\n**What's the core idea you're working on or thinking about?** Even if it's still rough, I'd love to hear:\\n- What do you actually DO (or want to do)?\\n- Who would benefit from it?\\n- What problem does it solve?\\n\\nThink of it this way—if you had 30 seconds to tell a friend what you're building, what would you say?\",\"examples\":[\"I'm building a meal-planning app for busy parents so they spend less time deciding what to cook\",\"I want to help freelancers find long-term clients instead of one-off gigs\",\"I'm creating a community platform where dog owners can share training tips and connect locally\"],\"conclusion\":\"You don't need to have it all figured out yet—just give me the raw idea, and we'll sharpen it together from there.\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1509,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":287,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
